# Plan to fix DataLoader ValueError

The user is encountering a `ValueError` because `prefetch_factor` is specified in `DataLoader` while `num_workers` is set to 0. PyTorch requires `num_workers > 0` for `prefetch_factor` and `persistent_workers` to be used.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component Name] ML Pipeline

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/main.py)

- Modify `DataLoader` instantiation to only include `prefetch_factor` and `persistent_workers` if `NUM_WORKERS > 0`.

#### [MODIFY] [eval.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/eval.py)

- Modify `DataLoader` instantiation to only include `prefetch_factor` and `persistent_workers` if `NUM_WORKERS > 0` (for robustness).

